query:
SELECT cs.sectionNumber, cs.sectionName, COUNT(cq.id) as questionCount 
FROM complianceSections cs 
LEFT JOIN complianceQuestions cq ON cs.id = cq.sectionId 
WHERE cs.sectionType = 'staff'
GROUP BY cs.id 
ORDER BY cs.sectionNumber
